parliamentary by-elections to the ruling Chama Cha Mapinduzi
party, the police said.
</P>
<P>
The Dar es Salaam Regional Police Commander, Alfred Gewe, said
that a group of people waving flags of the opposition party caused
extensive damages to properties belonging to the ruling party in a
riot between 5:30 p.m. and 8:30 p.m. Tuesday
</P>
<P>
