<HEADLINE> Landslide Kills 13 in Southwest China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, July 16 (Xinhua) -- A bus plunged over 100 meters
during a sudden landslide as it drove along a highway in the city
of Wanyuan in southwest China's Sichuan Province on Tuesday,
killing 13 people and seriously injuring 11 others.
</P>
