dollars on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The annual interbank rate of interest reduced to 5.9 percent in
the 24-hour term as compared with 6.05 on Wednesday. The peso
parity against the dollar maintained unchanged at 0.997 for
purchase and 1.002 for sale. 
